transcript.text: Hello everyone, in this video I'm very happy to share the new on Pin Shop and four over integrated web to pin platform.
It offers you the three key benefits.
You can transform your customer experience.
You can engage B to C and last B to B clients, offering your own in house produce product.
As well as offering the four over products.
You can also reduce the human dependency with an automated workflow and order submission.
So in three simple steps, you can become one stop web solution provider.
So let me show you how.
So very first thing is you can create your own online storefront with on Pin Shop.
You get a complete control over the UI UX to create the modern customer experience.
You can categorize the product according to your target audience.
And this product could be your produce in house products or directly fetch from the four over API.
Now here all the products can be even fetched from the four over API and you can even personalize the markups and give the user experience.
You can also utilize the on pin shop online designer studios and offered wide range of templates targeting to retail customers.

And if you're a marketing agency and commercial printers and having large B2B customers, you can also create private store friends, offer them fulfillment items or products like template based products so they can easily personalized.
So in three simple steps.
First of all you can fetch all the four over major categories in on print shop admin panel and then define your custom markup rules.
Markup rules can be based on the price and quantity.
So if you are getting more price from the customers you can also reduce the markup so you can create all those rules.
So for each category you can define which particular markup you want to apply.
Second for over product category has wide range of options and the nomen creature is also according to their target audience.
So for your customers you can change all the names and the descriptions what for over is offering in your storefront.
For example in this business card category there is a product type print method which is offset.
So I have completely disabled that option because as per my target audience in the storefront also for example these are the options like quoting sites.
So any of these options you find to change the names like the name of the 4 over option is colours packed.
But I have changed two sides.
So this particular option is called colours pack in four over but I have named it two sides because that is what my customers understand.
Third, from the product main category, I can also create multiple products.

So if I want to create a specific product like spot UV or a specific options, I can find that specific options from 4 over product category and then create a very combined or unique products from those multiple products with four over offers.
So from this category I'm showing you multiple products which we have created.
So certain products you have launched in your public site, certain products you can also offer to your B to B customers.
Even there is a shipping automation because four over has multiple facilities.
So if you have multiple products like your products you are shipping from your location as well as certain products are four over.
So end customer will be charged the shipping rates from the four over location plus your location.
So this would be an automation which is done in the back end and the third the automated submission because you have multiple products set up.
So system would automatically understand when somebody orders that this product is configured via 4 over API.

So automatically you would see that product listed in the four over order listing and once you submit the job it will also show you the four order details and order updates are automatically sent to the customer via auto e-mail notification in case if file has any issues.
And four over also has a preflight you can check and you can also re upload the file from the back end if customer have done any error.
So in these three simple steps, you can become the one stop web solution provider with this integrated platform.
Further, if you're interested to know more about this integrated solution, you can contact us at WWW dot on binshop.com.
